{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Akankah Film Marmalade Boy Tayang di Bioskop Indonesia?","content":"<p>Genre <em>romance</em> selalu menjadi pilihan paling populer, baik dalam film, anime, maupun manga. Itu karena <em>romance</em> dapat dipadukan dengan genre apapun. Untuk tipe cerita yang bergenre utama romance pun tak pernah kehabisan penggemar dari waktu ke waktu. Begitupun dengan film <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/list-komik-romantis-asal-jepang-yang-harus-kamu-baca/\">Marmalade Boy</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47679\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47679\" data-attachment-id=\"47679\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/01-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-47679 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Poster film Marmalade Boy (Sumber: Anime News Network)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47679\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Marmalade Boy (Sumber: Anime News Network)</p></div>\n<p>Jika kalian memang mengikuti manga bergenre romance, setidaknya pernah mendengar judul manga lawas ini. Marmalade Boy bercerita tentang gadis remaja bernama Miki Koishikawa yang menikmati kehidupan yang tenang. Namun hidupnya mulai menghadapi masalah yang tak terduga sepulang kedua orangtuanya berlibur dari Hawaii. Orangtua Miki mengumukan kepada anaknya kalau mereka akan bercerai. Mereka juga akan bertukar pasangan dengan keluarga Matsuura yang mereka temui semasa liburan di Hawaii.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vOI7oEr5rcs\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Lantaran ingin melibatkan Miki dalam setiap keputusan yang diambil, kedua pasangan yang saling bertukar itu mengadakan makan malam bersama. Ketika Miki merasa sudah mempersiapkan mentalnya kepada dua orangtua barunya, Miki kembali menghadapi kenyataan tidak terduga. Di sanalah dia bertemu pertama kali dengan Yuu, remaja tampan anak dari keluarga Matsuura. Itulah awal perkenalan Miki dengan Yuu. Tak cukup sampai di situ, kedua orangtua mereka pun mengumumkan akan tinggal di rumah yang sama, dan berarti Miki dan Yuu akan bertemu tiap hari. Lantaran tinggal satu atap, rasa cinta perlahan tumbuh dalam diri Miki dan Yuu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47680\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47680\" data-attachment-id=\"47680\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/02-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47680\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Yuu main ke kamar Miki, mau ngapain ya? (Sumber: Youtube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Yuu main ke kamar Miki, mau ngapain ya? (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div>\n<p>Marmalade Boy pertama kali diluncurkan pada tahun 1992 di majalah Ribon milik Shueisha. Manga karya Wataru Yoshizumi ini meraih kepopuleran pada zamannya sehingga dibuatkan adaptasi serial animenya pada tahun 1994, menyusul adaptasi anime versi film pada 1995.</p>\n<p>Setelah 26 tahun semenjak peluncuran manga perdananya, film Marmalade Boy versi <em>Live-Action</em> ditayangkan di seluruh bioskop Jepang pada 27 April lalu dan menyedot perhatian para penggila genre <em>romance</em> sehingga menempati posisi ke-8 dalam penayangan di minggu perdananya. Sutradara Yuichi Hiroki—yang pernah menangani adaptasi<em> Live-Action</em> manga bergenre <em>romance</em> lainnya seperti Wolf Girl &amp; Black Prince—terpilih untuk menangani film ini, dibantu dengan Taeko Asano sebagai penulis skenario.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47682\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47682\" data-attachment-id=\"47682\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/03a-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03a-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47682\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Yuu sedang berkutat di dapur. Tampan ya. (Sumber: Natalie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03a-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47682\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Yuu sedang berkutat di dapur. Tampan ya. (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Dari deretan pemain, Ryo Yoshizawa—aktor yang pernah bekerja sama dengan Yuichi Hiroki di film Strobe Edge dan berperan di <em>Live-Action</em> Gintama, Bleach, Saiki Kusuo, dan Ao Haru Ride—menjadi Yuu Matsuura. Sedangkan yang berperan sebagai Miki Koishikawa adalah Hinako Sakurai, aktris manis pendatang baru.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47681\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47681\" data-attachment-id=\"47681\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/03-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47681\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Miki sedang menikmati sarapan. Yummy! (Sumber: Natalie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47681\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Miki sedang menikmati sarapan. Yummy! (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Tak hanya mengambil dua aktor dan aktris muda saja, pemeran orangtua Yuu dan Miki pun tak kalah penting. Rei Dan berperan sebagai Rumi Koishikawa, ibu kandung Miki. Sementara yang menjadi Jin Koishikawa, ayah kandung Miki adalah Michitaka Tsutsui. Di kelaurga Matsuura, Miho Nakayama berperan menjadi Ibu kandung Yuu, Chiyako Matsuura. Lawan mainnya adalah Shosuke Tanihara, yang menjadi Yoji Matsuura, ayah kandung Yuu. Peranan keempat orangtua ini begitu penting karena dari merekalah semua permasalahan berawal.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47683\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47683\" data-attachment-id=\"47683\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/04-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47683\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Miki dan Yuu, romantis bukan? (Sumber: Natalie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47683\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Miki dan Yuu, romantis bukan? (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Ada pula pemeran-pemeran pendukung lain seperti Taiko Sato yang menjadi Ginta Suo, teman sekelas Yuu dan Miki yang memendam perasaan terhadap Miki. Ada pula Niina Endo, yang menjadi mantan kekasih Yuu, Arimi Suzuki. Sementara itu Meiko Akizuki, sahabat karib Miki, akan diperankan oleh Mio Yuki.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_47684\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47684\" data-attachment-id=\"47684\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-marmalade-boy-bioskop-indonesia/attachment/05-marmalade-boy/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-marmalade-boy\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47684\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy.jpg\" alt=\"Keluarga Yuu dan Miki (Sumber: Natalie)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-marmalade-boy-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47684\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Keluarga Yuu dan Miki (Sumber: Natalie)</p></div>\n<p>Untuk lagu tema akan dibawakan oleh GReeeeN, berjudul Koi. Kalian ada yang ingin mendengarkan lagunya? Bisa disimak dalam video klip berikut:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PglnMmiPDps\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Nah, kalian ada yang penasaran dan ingin segera menonton filmnya? Sabar dulu. Karena banyak sekali film Jepang yang akan tayang dalam waktu dekat, mungkin Marmalade Boy harus menunggu antrian terlebih dahulu.</p>\n<p>Tapi yang pasti, film ini memiliki segmen penggemarnya sendiri, sehingga pasti ada yang menontonnya. Apalagi masyarakat Indonesia menyukai genre <em>romance</em>. Nggak percaya? Cek daftar komik yang ada di <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> aja. Genre <em>romance</em> pasti selalu banyak yang <em>subscribe</em> dan <em>like</em>. Maka yakinlah kalau film ini bisa tayang di Indonesia. Hehe.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a54c4ff1-c237-5ed2-a013-ab8713bccf10"}}}